channel.title: Project Vapor. Beta Testing open to the public
channel.description:
Hello there, this is Project Vapor. here is a virus scan just because i know that people like to claim it's a virus, even thou its a .jar file.
[url=https://www.virustotal.com/en/file/c66e233a61112dbd06c171c91a6e898035dea616eb5e573763f7f18e9eff5cb3/analysis/1396398549/]https://www.virustotal.com/en/file/c66e233a61112dbd06c171c91a6e898035dea616eb5e573763f7f18e9eff5cb3/analysis/1396398549/[/url] [SIZE=3]Server Information.[/SIZE] It is an economy based server. its a 317. with a new packed cache. in beta mode, there are bugs in the server. im am working to fix them. running off an vps, if need be i will upgrade the vps when it comes out of beta. very mature owner, ill tell you a little about myself. i get on and interact with the players, i wont ignore you just because your just a normal player. i have been in your shoes, and i know how it feels. im 20 years old. im a united states soldier. i do not care about donations. as i get paid to be a soldier, which in other terms. i can pay for the server out of pocket. this is a server for the players. i will try my best to put out updates that the players want. [SIZE=3]Well lets get to some pics.[/SIZE]
